  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育场景的序列图，展示Swaparoo平台如何启动一个LMS门户实例。核心角色包括Voter1作为终端用户，Core组件负责部署，Zoe作为中间协调层，还有一个委员会节点Ctee负责学生数据库的初始化。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Voter1",
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到Core有两个标签：swaparoo和brdeployer，Ctee也有swaparoo和brcommittee。这些标签需要显示在参与者框里吗？还有，流程的起点是Core向Zoe发起startInstance调用吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "swaparoo",
        "brdeployer",
        "brcommittee"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，标签都要保留。流程从Core触发Zoe的startInstance开始，然后Zoe去启动学生数据库，Ctee返回LMS门户配置给Zoe，Zoe再回传内容CDN地址给Core。之后Core向委员会获取选民邀请列表，最后把邀请发给Voter1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "Voter1",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "getVoterInvitations",
        "invitationV1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把四个参与者按顺序排好：Voter1作为actor在最左，然后是Core、Zoe、Ctee。第一步画了Core到Zoe的startInstance消息，标注了Education_LMS_Portal参数。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Voter1",
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "startInstance",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，Zoe启动学生数据库那一步，返回值的写法我有点犹豫。是写成{Education_StudentDB}还是其他格式？另外Core调用getVoterInvitations的时候，前面有个E(Education_ClassroomService)的前缀，这个要保留。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Core",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "getVoterInvitations"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到。Zoe到Ctee的start消息返回{Education_StudentDB}，Ctee回Zoe是{Education_LMS_Portal}，Zoe回Core是{Education_ContentCDN}。然后Core到Ctee的消息写成E(Education_ClassroomService).getVoterInvitations(Education_LMS_Portal)，返回[Education_LMS_Portal]数组，最后Core发invitationV1给Voter1。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
